Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.68,0:00:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能 那傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地之…一族嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.44,0:00:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.47,0:00:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.92,0:00:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 那不是夢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.61,0:01:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.35,0:01:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.51,0:01:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 曉 妾身是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.90,0:01:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米娜…公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.50,0:01:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的全名是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.62,0:01:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉·鏑木·烈根多夫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.43,0:01:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真正的身份是？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.19,0:01:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人狼騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.86,0:01:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是地之一族
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.34,0:01:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.31,0:01:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.09,0:01:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖這麼說 但已經是中午了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.49,0:01:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.18,0:01:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妾身的女僕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.85,0:01:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 奈麗 奈拉 奈羅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.27,0:01:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.83,0:01:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.78,0:02:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您礙事了 請移開您的手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.31,0:02:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我自己能幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.57,0:02:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是打算不讓我工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.35,0:02:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 公主 快做些什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.45,0:02:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來 這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.09,0:02:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣 適合我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.70,0:02:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 你那打扮…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.97,0:02:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不肯定的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 襲擊了平穩的午後的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴天霹靂來著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.43,0:02:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾名米娜·柴佩西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有緣而來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.84,0:02:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想請各位貴人多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.68,0:02:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.17,0:02:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以這天為界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的學院 成了吸血鬼們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不斷巡迴舞動迴旋曲的舞台之一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#03 Teen Wolf
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸血鬼的王？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來她是高中生來著的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.19,0:04:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…你的座位就安排在…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅拉修女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.17,0:04:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這麼害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會突然咬你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為妾身的僕從就就讀於這個班級吶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.79,0:04:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能把我的座位安排在那個人旁邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕從…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鏑木曉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎哎——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.13,0:04:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修女 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:05:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天只是打算過來打個招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.81,0:05:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就此告辭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.31,0:05:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曉 等會你也來理事長室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.09,0:05:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…吸血鬼的侍從？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.57,0:05:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 給我說明清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.02,0:05:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天明明還說沒興趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們滾一邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.54,0:05:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這種事怎麼能讓人默默接受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.78,0:05:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯啊 詳細說明給我們聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.72,0:05:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗手間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.38,0:05:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 曉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三枝同學 你從曉那裡聽說過些什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自學生會 通知全學生會要員
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.93,0:06:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現起 將進行緊急學生會要員會議
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全要員及執行部員 請速集合至學生會室
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.55,0:06:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三枝同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複 自學生會 通…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.70,0:06:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要別人說明的明明是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.30,0:06:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算記憶回來了 但也不是全部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年 就是你17歲的生日了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.25,0:06:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵從舊約聖經
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你將成為公主殿下的侍從
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.90,0:06:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而在其身邊侍奉其左右
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這任務 是測試你是否能勝任其的試金石
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.06,0:06:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竭盡全力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.27,0:06:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 我明白的啦 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.82,0:06:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…大概在那之後…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.09,0:06:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 可惡 還記不清
